name: Melancholy Hill
description:
The artwork story :

a lonely woman who falls in love with someone she can't have. Plastic trees are something organic that has been faked, in the sense that while it's not what they want, it's at least a 'medicine'. instead of going after what she couldn't have, she fell in love with someone else.
